# (SNOMED CT Affiliate License, ICD-10-TM, TMT/TMLT, LOINC, DrugBank/PrimeKG, UMLS)
*.rf2
**/snomed_*release*/
snomed*Snapshot*/
icd10tm*
icd-10-tm*
tmt_release*
tmlt_release*
*loinc*release*
LoincTableCore*
drugbank*.xml
drugbank*.csv
primekg_*.csv
kg_raw*.csv

